  "original_title": "\u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0db4\u0dd4\u0dbb \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dcf.\u0dbd\u0dda \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dda \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db0\u0dcf\u0db1 \u0db4\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0db1 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0db0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d9d\u0dcf\u0dad\u0db1\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The chief administrative officer of the Lankapura district office is killed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Lankapura Police say that the chief administrative officer of the Polonnaruwa Lankapura Divisional Secretariat was hacked to death with sharp weapons at her home at around 2.30 this morning.",
        "According to the investigating police, the person who has been murdered is ML Yamuna Patmini, a 42-year-old mother of two who resided at Talpotha Polonnaru address.",
        "Police say that the regional secretary's husband and two children were present when she was killed.",
        "The Lankapura police say that they have started preliminary investigations to find out who might have killed her and for what reason.",
        "Further investigations related to the incident are being carried out by a team of special police officers as per the instructions of Polonnaruwa Senior Superintendent of Police Mr. Oshan Hewawitharana."
      ],
